{"id": "49782", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49782", "title": "H'rothgar Firehammer", "text": "H'rothgar Firehammer is a dwarven male fighter in the &lt;a href=\"Five%20Flagons%20Inn\"&gt;Five Flagons Inn&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Bridge%20District\"&gt;Bridge District&lt;/a&gt;. He is clad in enchanted Chain Mail and holds a War hammer. The dwarf has some dialogue if you speak with him. He appears to be focused on his grog, and not particularly engaging beyond his drink. \nMod content.\n&lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; revises H'rothgar by assigning an SCS default fighter AI script for smarter tactical behavior and potion use. Weapon proficiency is changed to 4 pips with War hammer and 2 pips in single weapon fighting style. Random SCS treasures are placed in his inventory."}
