{"id": "10225", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10225", "title": "Hall of Wonders", "text": "The Hall of Wonders is a building in the &lt;a href=\"West%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;western district&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; and serves as a museum for all kinds of inventions. One of the containers contains a &lt;a href=\"telescope\"&gt;telescope&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe two center display cases contain a &lt;a href=\"Star%20Sapphire\"&gt;Star Sapphire&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Rogue%20Stone\"&gt;Rogue Stone&lt;/a&gt;, respectively."}
