{"id": "38492", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38492", "title": "Tombelthen's Journal (second half)", "text": "This is the second half of a journal belonging to a mithral prospector named Idras Tombelthen, detailing where he hid his findings. It is useless without the &lt;a href=\"Tombelthen%27s%20Journal%20%28first%20half%29\"&gt;first half&lt;/a&gt; of the journal.\nAcquisition.\nThis half of Tombelthen's journal can be found in the &lt;a href=\"Ruined%20Temple\"&gt;Ruined Temple&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". It is concealed in a bundle of rubble in the cell where &lt;a href=\"Mazzy%20Fentan\"&gt;Mazzy Fentan&lt;/a&gt; is imprisoned.\nUse.\nAlthough this half of Tombelthen's Journal can be located by anyone, it is actually tied to the &lt;a href=\"stronghold\"&gt;stronghold&lt;/a&gt; quests for the &lt;a href=\"Ranger\"&gt;Ranger&lt;/a&gt;, and is useless to any version of &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; who does not belong to that class.\nThe first of the three quests that collectively make up &lt;a href=\"Ranger-Protector%20of%20the%20Umar%20Hills\"&gt;Ranger-Protector of the Umar Hills&lt;/a&gt; will see Gorion's Ward confronted by &lt;a href=\"Lord%20Igen%20Tombelthen\"&gt;Lord Igen Tombelthen&lt;/a&gt;, who is ravaging the forest to discover the mithral concealed by his deceased ancestor. He will give them the first half of the journal, which combined with this one allows them to locate the &lt;a href=\"Mithral%20Medallion\"&gt;Mithral Medallion&lt;/a&gt; hidden by Idras Tombelthen."}
