\"&gt;Potion of Healing&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Invisibility\"&gt;Potion of Invisibility&lt;/a&gt;, and 86 . The chest of drawers in the small bedroom is locked and empty.\nBeginning near the stairs and moving left to right, the first seven bookshelves contain copies of the &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20Shadowdale%20I\"&gt;History of Shadowdale I&lt;/a&gt; thru &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20Shadowdale%20VII\"&gt;History of Shadowdale VII&lt;/a&gt; and the last two are empty.\nNotes.\n\"Travenhurst Manor\" and the &lt;a href=\"Manor%20House\"&gt;Manor House&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Nashkel\"&gt;Nashkel&lt;/a&gt; have identical interior maps for both floors."}
