{"id": "46611", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46611", "title": "Tremain Belde'ar's Home", "text": "Tremain Belde'ar's Home is the home of &lt;a href=\"Tremain%20Belde%27ar\"&gt;Tremain Belde'ar&lt;/a&gt; and is located just north of &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%27s%20Hall\"&gt;The Lady's Hall&lt;/a&gt; near the western wall in the district of &lt;a href=\"West%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;West Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;. The front door is unlocked.\nThe ground floor is unpopulated. The chest is locked with a DC of 30 and contains a &lt;a href=\"Bluestone%20Necklace\"&gt;Bluestone Necklace&lt;/a&gt;. The bookshelves contain copies of the &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Sisters%20of%20Light%20and%20Darkness\"&gt;History of the Sisters of Light and Darkness&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Unicorn%20Run\"&gt;History of the Unicorn Run&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe second floor is populated at night by a sleeping halfling and a sleeping man. The unlocked chest of drawers contains a copy of the &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Ulgarth\"&gt;History of the Ulgarth&lt;/a&gt; and 22 . The bookshelves contain copies of the &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Western%20Heartlands\"&gt;History of the Western Heartlands&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Zhentarim\"&gt;History of the Zhentarim&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "49954", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49954", "title": "Treya", "text": "The Sun Soul Monk Treya is a character from .\nGameplay.\nTreya is one of four Sun Soul Monks who confront the party and state that Rasaad is a known murderer. Various dialogue options are presented. These dialogue selections will determine the direction of the encounter in the Wilderness. \nTreya has all the abilities, immunities and special bonuses afforded to a Sun Soul Monk kit commensurate with her 10th Level experience. She wears the Cloak of Unerring Strikes.\nIn battle she will quaff a &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Extra%20Healing\"&gt;Potion of Extra Healing&lt;/a&gt; when damaged to a 50% threshold and may consume a &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Freedom\"&gt;Potion of Freedom&lt;/a&gt; when an enemy is detected at a certain distance.\nA &lt;a href=\"Lay%20On%20Hands%20%28monk%29\"&gt;Lay On Hands (monk)&lt;/a&gt; ability is used if original HP damage exceeds 60%.\nShe fights with her hands and feet in melee combat.\nShe'll possibly enable the &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fists\"&gt;Flaming Fists&lt;/a&gt; spell ability when opponents are detected at a specific range.\nA &lt;a href=\"Sun%20Soulbeam\"&gt;Sun Soulbeam&lt;/a&gt; may be attempted if an opponent is in range and has less than 50% Magic or Fire resistance - and later a &lt;a href=\"Greater%20Sun\"&gt;Greater Sun&lt;/a&gt; if a target is within 30'."}
