{"id": "56400", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=56400", "title": "Unlocking the Final Seal", "text": "Unlocking the Final Seal is a side quest available and .\nThe quest is a \"side quest\" because all content in &lt;a href=\"Watcher%27s%20Keep\"&gt;Watcher's Keep&lt;/a&gt; is optional and not mandatory to complete the main story - however, this quest is mandatory if attempting to complete the Watcher's Keep storyline.\nAcquisition.\nThe quest is initially registered in the player's journal by engaging with the &lt;a href=\"Helmite%20Ghost\"&gt;Helmite Ghost&lt;/a&gt;, or the &lt;a href=\"Globe%20Machine\"&gt;Globe Machine&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteracting with &lt;a href=\"The%20Spirit%20Altar\"&gt;The Spirit Altar&lt;/a&gt; won't register the quest unless the party has possession of the &lt;a href=\"Warrior%27s%20Skull\"&gt;Warrior's Skull&lt;/a&gt;, which can only be obtained by engaging with the Helmite Ghost.\nIt is probably optimal to start with the Helmite Ghost first when exploring and solving the Final Seal.\nRegistering the quest.\nIf the player engages with any of the three challenge options, the quest is registered into the journal, as follows:\nCompleting the Helmite Ghost's challenges.\nAfter completing all three challenges required by the Helmite Ghost and obtaining the &lt;a href=\"Heart%20Key\"&gt;Heart Key&lt;/a&gt; - the player's journal updates, as follows:\nCompleting the Globe Machine challenge.\nAfter the party correctly places all the colored globes in the correct colored containers and obtains the &lt;a href=\"Mind%20Key\"&gt;Mind Key&lt;/a&gt; - the player's journal updates, as follows:\nCompleting the Spirit Warrior's challenge.\nAfter completing the Spirit Warrior adventure challenges and obtaining the &lt;a href=\"Spirit%20Key\"&gt;Spirit Key&lt;/a&gt; - the player's journal updates, as follows:\nCompleting the quest.\nWhen the party has unlocked each pedestal adjacent to the final seal (and by extension faced the various guardians), then the party may turn the wheel to open the final seal.\nTurning the wheel displays a text, reading:\nThis triggers the final journal entry for the quest, as follows:\nThe player's journal is updated, certain entries are removed, and the quest is marked as finished.\nThe party may now transition through the new portal leading below when ready to do so."}
