{"id": "49931", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49931", "title": "Vagrant Blades", "text": "The Vagrant Blades is a group of Adventurers found in . They are located in the Southeast portion of the &lt;a href=\"Abandoned%20Amphitheater\"&gt;Abandoned Amphitheater&lt;/a&gt; map, adjacent to some ruins where there was a Dungeon Entrance (now sealed by some kind of tunnel collapse). \nGameplay.\nThis band of adventurer's is arguing over a rare piece of loot found inside, a Belt with some kind of power. If you get close enough to the group, there will be a series of dialogue choices you may engage in. \nThe outcome of the encounter depends on your choices and what you say. Like your own party, this group has also accumulated experience and magical items to use in offensive and defensive actions. So there are risks and rewards if you choose to take them on in a hostile manner."}
