{"id": "14751", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14751", "title": "Valygar's Body", "text": "Valygar's Body will be obtained if &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; decides to kill &lt;a href=\"Valygar%20Corthala\"&gt;Valygar Corthala&lt;/a&gt; in the quest &lt;a href=\"The%20hunt%20for%20Valygar%20Corthala\"&gt;The hunt for Valygar Corthala&lt;/a&gt;. It can brought to &lt;a href=\"Tolgerias\"&gt;Tolgerias&lt;/a&gt; to end the quest, but one will not then be able to use it to access the &lt;a href=\"The%20Planar%20Sphere\"&gt;Planar Sphere&lt;/a&gt;. One can also enter the sphere by taking him there alive as a party member."}
