{"id": "39490", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39490", "title": "Second Stone Fragment", "text": "The Second Stone Fragment is held by &lt;a href=\"Deneld\"&gt;Deneld&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragonspear%20Castle%20Exterior\"&gt;outside of Dragonspear Castle&lt;/a&gt;. The party can convince Deneld to hand over the fragment in a variety of ways:\nOtherwise it can simply be stolen.\nIf you take this fragment and the &lt;a href=\"First%20Stone%20Fragment\"&gt;other stone fragment&lt;/a&gt; to priestess of &lt;a href=\"Tempus\"&gt;Tempus&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Mizhena\"&gt;Mizhena&lt;/a&gt;, she can bless them, which combines both fragments into the &lt;a href=\"Sanctified%20Shards\"&gt;Sanctified Shards&lt;/a&gt;. The Sanctified Shards are needed for the &lt;a href=\"Foehammer%27s%20Blessing\"&gt;Foehammer's Blessing&lt;/a&gt; quest in ."}
